 
<p>
The
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2023/apr/25/carbon-dioxide-removal-tech-polarising-climate-science">controversy over possible future technologies</a>
for removing CO2 from the air.
<p>
I think that we should try to develop CO2 removal technology, because
it will be very helpful if it does work efficiently; but it would be a
terrible mistake to bet on that.  Our investment now should go mainly
into replacing fossil fuels.

